N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 9 ยง 459.2 - Types of snowmobile equipment and operations requiring approval

State Regulations

The following types of snowmobile equipment must be
approved: (a) Mufflers. (b) Noise emission from the entire
snowmobile. Notes
